HEADWORD: Referee
<hw>Ref`er*ee"</hw> <pr>(-<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One to whom a
thing is referred; a person to whom a matter in dispute has been
referred, in order that he may settle it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Judge; arbitrator; umpire. See
<er>Judge</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

